{
  "video_id": "JlxJYSFPpQo",
  "method": "api",
  "language": null,
  "duration_seconds": 1.9913328000111505,
  "entry_count": 296,
  "error": null,
  "entries": [
    {
      "time": "00:00",
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.04,
      "duration": 2.04,
      "text": "- [Instructor] You know what\nI always wondered as a kid?"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:02",
      "start": 2.04,
      "end": 5.13,
      "duration": 3.09,
      "text": "When I took my car and\ndashed it into a wall,"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:05",
      "start": 5.13,
      "end": 7.02,
      "duration": 1.89,
      "text": "it would just immediately\ngo and bounce back"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:07",
      "start": 7.02,
      "end": 8.61,
      "duration": 1.59,
      "text": "and nothing would happen to it."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:08",
      "start": 8.61,
      "end": 11.34,
      "duration": 2.73,
      "text": "But real cars are very different."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:11",
      "start": 11.34,
      "end": 14.37,
      "duration": 3.03,
      "text": "Real cars are so fragile\nthat even at modest speed,"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:14",
      "start": 14.37,
      "end": 17.82,
      "duration": 3.45,
      "text": "if you were to go and ram\ninto this no-parking board,"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:17",
      "start": 17.82,
      "end": 21.63,
      "duration": 3.81,
      "text": "then it would very easily get\ndented, damaged, and whatnot."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:21",
      "start": 21.63,
      "end": 23.46,
      "duration": 1.83,
      "text": "Well, I used to wonder why real vehicles"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:23",
      "start": 23.46,
      "end": 25.830000000000002,
      "duration": 2.37,
      "text": "are not made with much stronger materials"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:25",
      "start": 25.83,
      "end": 28.11,
      "duration": 2.28,
      "text": "that ensures that none of this happens."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:28",
      "start": 28.11,
      "end": 29.07,
      "duration": 0.96,
      "text": "Well, guess what?"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:29",
      "start": 29.07,
      "end": 31.05,
      "duration": 1.98,
      "text": "Turns out this is a deliberate choice."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:31",
      "start": 31.05,
      "end": 33.99,
      "duration": 2.94,
      "text": "We deliberately make sure\nthat vehicles easily crumple,"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:33",
      "start": 33.99,
      "end": 35.79,
      "duration": 1.8,
      "text": "they get easily damaged."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:35",
      "start": 35.79,
      "end": 36.99,
      "duration": 1.2,
      "text": "Why, you ask?"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:36",
      "start": 36.99,
      "end": 38.88,
      "duration": 1.89,
      "text": "Because that actually makes things safer"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:38",
      "start": 38.88,
      "end": 40.68,
      "duration": 1.8,
      "text": "for the people sitting inside."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:40",
      "start": 40.68,
      "end": 41.513,
      "duration": 0.833,
      "text": "But how?"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:41",
      "start": 41.513,
      "end": 44.339999999999996,
      "duration": 2.827,
      "text": "How does that make things safer\nfor people sitting inside?"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:44",
      "start": 44.34,
      "end": 45.612,
      "duration": 1.272,
      "text": "Well, one way to answer that question"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:45",
      "start": 45.612,
      "end": 49.17,
      "duration": 3.558,
      "text": "is by introducing a new\nquantity called impulse,"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:49",
      "start": 49.17,
      "end": 52.08,
      "duration": 2.91,
      "text": "and that's what we're\ngonna do in this video."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:52",
      "start": 52.08,
      "end": 53.339999999999996,
      "duration": 1.26,
      "text": "So let's begin."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:53",
      "start": 53.34,
      "end": 54.6,
      "duration": 1.26,
      "text": "So where do we start?"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:54",
      "start": 54.6,
      "end": 56.79,
      "duration": 2.19,
      "text": "Well, we'll start with\nNewton's Second Law,"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:56",
      "start": 56.79,
      "end": 58.769999999999996,
      "duration": 1.98,
      "text": "the cornerstone of our physics, right?"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:58",
      "start": 58.77,
      "end": 60.510000000000005,
      "duration": 1.74,
      "text": "So Newton's Second Law can be written as,"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:00",
      "start": 60.51,
      "end": 61.65,
      "duration": 1.14,
      "text": "we've seen this in the previous video,"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:01",
      "start": 61.65,
      "end": 64.62,
      "duration": 2.97,
      "text": "we can write it as net\nforce are acting on a body"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:04",
      "start": 64.62,
      "end": 68.34,
      "duration": 3.72,
      "text": "equals rate of change, sorry,\nlet's use a different color,"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:08",
      "start": 68.34,
      "end": 72.06,
      "duration": 3.72,
      "text": "okay, rate of change of momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "01:12",
      "start": 72.06,
      "end": 74.34,
      "duration": 2.28,
      "text": "This means if there's a\nlot of change in momentum"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:14",
      "start": 74.34,
      "end": 75.33,
      "duration": 0.99,
      "text": "per second,"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:15",
      "start": 75.33,
      "end": 78.03,
      "duration": 2.7,
      "text": "then there must be a big\nnet force acting on it,"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:18",
      "start": 78.03,
      "end": 81.33,
      "duration": 3.3,
      "text": "and if there's a very tiny\nchange in momentum per second,"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:21",
      "start": 81.33,
      "end": 83.73,
      "duration": 2.4,
      "text": "there must be a very\nsmall force acting on it."
    },
    {
      "time": "01:23",
      "start": 83.73,
      "end": 85.498,
      "duration": 1.768,
      "text": "Now let's rearrange this."
    },
    {
      "time": "01:25",
      "start": 85.498,
      "end": 89.7,
      "duration": 4.202,
      "text": "Let's multiply by the time,\ndelta T, on both sides."
    },
    {
      "time": "01:29",
      "start": 89.7,
      "end": 93.57000000000001,
      "duration": 3.87,
      "text": "So if you do that, we\nwill now get a net force"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:33",
      "start": 93.57,
      "end": 97.27,
      "duration": 3.7,
      "text": "multiplied by the time over\nwhich that force is acting"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:37",
      "start": 97.27,
      "end": 102.27,
      "duration": 5.0,
      "text": "equals the change in momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "01:43",
      "start": 103.83,
      "end": 105.813,
      "duration": 1.983,
      "text": "And we're gonna box this."
    },
    {
      "time": "01:47",
      "start": 107.13,
      "end": 108.33,
      "duration": 1.2,
      "text": "You know why?"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:48",
      "start": 108.33,
      "end": 112.182,
      "duration": 3.852,
      "text": "Because this quantity on the left side"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:52",
      "start": 112.182,
      "end": 115.56,
      "duration": 3.378,
      "text": "is what we call impulse."
    },
    {
      "time": "01:55",
      "start": 115.56,
      "end": 117.45,
      "duration": 1.89,
      "text": "Now the first question\nthat could come to our mind"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:57",
      "start": 117.45,
      "end": 118.92,
      "duration": 1.47,
      "text": "is why do we do this?"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:58",
      "start": 118.92,
      "end": 121.83,
      "duration": 2.91,
      "text": "Like why are we just\nrearranging that same equation"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:01",
      "start": 121.83,
      "end": 125.859,
      "duration": 4.029,
      "text": "and now calling this a new\nquantity, calling it impulse?"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:05",
      "start": 125.859,
      "end": 127.05,
      "duration": 1.191,
      "text": "(chuckles) Why do we do that?"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:07",
      "start": 127.05,
      "end": 129.06,
      "duration": 2.01,
      "text": "Well, the short answer is because"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:09",
      "start": 129.06,
      "end": 132.69,
      "duration": 3.63,
      "text": "it helps us gain a new\nperspective of that same equation."
    },
    {
      "time": "02:12",
      "start": 132.69,
      "end": 135.45,
      "duration": 2.76,
      "text": "Some perspectives are\nuseful in some scenarios,"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:15",
      "start": 135.45,
      "end": 138.03,
      "duration": 2.58,
      "text": "other perspectives could be\nuseful in some other scenarios."
    },
    {
      "time": "02:18",
      "start": 138.03,
      "end": 140.01,
      "duration": 1.98,
      "text": "And we will see how this impulse idea"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:20",
      "start": 140.01,
      "end": 142.89,
      "duration": 2.88,
      "text": "is so useful in some\nspecific scenarios over here."
    },
    {
      "time": "02:22",
      "start": 142.89,
      "end": 145.85999999999999,
      "duration": 2.97,
      "text": "But anyways, let's try to\nlearn more about impulse."
    },
    {
      "time": "02:25",
      "start": 145.86,
      "end": 147.87,
      "duration": 2.01,
      "text": "We can immediately see from this equation"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:27",
      "start": 147.87,
      "end": 152.46,
      "duration": 4.59,
      "text": "that impulse will always\nequal the change in momentum,"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:32",
      "start": 152.46,
      "end": 153.54000000000002,
      "duration": 1.08,
      "text": "right?"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:33",
      "start": 153.54,
      "end": 157.23,
      "duration": 3.69,
      "text": "Impulse equals change in momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "02:37",
      "start": 157.23,
      "end": 159.845,
      "duration": 2.615,
      "text": "That's the perspective\nwe're looking for, actually."
    },
    {
      "time": "02:39",
      "start": 159.845,
      "end": 162.42,
      "duration": 2.575,
      "text": "And we'll take some examples in a while,"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:42",
      "start": 162.42,
      "end": 165.03,
      "duration": 2.61,
      "text": "but before we do that, can\nwe talk about its units?"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:45",
      "start": 165.03,
      "end": 166.2,
      "duration": 1.17,
      "text": "Whenever we learn a new quantity,"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:46",
      "start": 166.2,
      "end": 167.42999999999998,
      "duration": 1.23,
      "text": "we should try and identify its units."
    },
    {
      "time": "02:47",
      "start": 167.43,
      "end": 168.84,
      "duration": 1.41,
      "text": "Can you identify its units?"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:48",
      "start": 168.84,
      "end": 172.86,
      "duration": 4.02,
      "text": "All right, since impulse is\nthe product of force and time,"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:52",
      "start": 172.86,
      "end": 174.93,
      "duration": 2.07,
      "text": "well, the unit of force would be newtons"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:54",
      "start": 174.93,
      "end": 177.81,
      "duration": 2.88,
      "text": "and the unit of time would be seconds."
    },
    {
      "time": "02:57",
      "start": 177.81,
      "end": 180.12,
      "duration": 2.31,
      "text": "So we could say it is newton-seconds."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:00",
      "start": 180.12,
      "end": 182.25,
      "duration": 2.13,
      "text": "I could also, for example,\nsubstitute for newton."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:02",
      "start": 182.25,
      "end": 185.94,
      "duration": 3.69,
      "text": "Remember newton, which\nis force is F equals MA,"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:05",
      "start": 185.94,
      "end": 190.05,
      "duration": 4.11,
      "text": "which means newton should\nbe M, which is kilograms,"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:10",
      "start": 190.05,
      "end": 192.33,
      "duration": 2.28,
      "text": "and A, which is meters per second squared."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:12",
      "start": 192.33,
      "end": 193.89000000000001,
      "duration": 1.56,
      "text": "So let me just write that down."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:13",
      "start": 193.89,
      "end": 197.13299999999998,
      "duration": 3.243,
      "text": "Meters per second squared."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:17",
      "start": 197.97,
      "end": 202.08,
      "duration": 4.11,
      "text": "So this should be your\nnewtons multiplied by seconds."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:22",
      "start": 202.08,
      "end": 203.10000000000002,
      "duration": 1.02,
      "text": "Seconds cancels out."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:23",
      "start": 203.1,
      "end": 206.13,
      "duration": 3.03,
      "text": "And we can also say it is\nkilograms meters per second."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:26",
      "start": 206.13,
      "end": 209.164,
      "duration": 3.034,
      "text": "And that's nice because that\nis the unit of momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:29",
      "start": 209.164,
      "end": 210.75,
      "duration": 1.586,
      "text": "(chuckles) Remember?"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:30",
      "start": 210.75,
      "end": 215.54,
      "duration": 4.79,
      "text": "Momentum is MV, M times V."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:36",
      "start": 216.677,
      "end": 220.23,
      "duration": 3.553,
      "text": "And look, the unit of\nmomentum is kilograms,"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:40",
      "start": 220.23,
      "end": 221.51999999999998,
      "duration": 1.29,
      "text": "meters per second."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:41",
      "start": 221.52,
      "end": 223.23000000000002,
      "duration": 1.71,
      "text": "And that's nice because we just saw"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:43",
      "start": 223.23,
      "end": 225.17999999999998,
      "duration": 1.95,
      "text": "impulse equals change in momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:45",
      "start": 225.18,
      "end": 227.13,
      "duration": 1.95,
      "text": "So the unit of impulse should be the same"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:47",
      "start": 227.13,
      "end": 228.6,
      "duration": 1.47,
      "text": "as the unit of momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:48",
      "start": 228.6,
      "end": 229.433,
      "duration": 0.833,
      "text": "And that's what we see,"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:49",
      "start": 229.433,
      "end": 233.13,
      "duration": 3.697,
      "text": "the unit of impulse is the\nsame as unit of momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:53",
      "start": 233.13,
      "end": 234.78,
      "duration": 1.65,
      "text": "Makes sense, right?"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:54",
      "start": 234.78,
      "end": 237.36,
      "duration": 2.58,
      "text": "Now to see the power of\nthis new perspective,"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:57",
      "start": 237.36,
      "end": 238.65,
      "duration": 1.29,
      "text": "let's take a scenario."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:58",
      "start": 238.65,
      "end": 242.55,
      "duration": 3.9,
      "text": "Imagine we have two toy cars\nfitted with rocket engines."
    },
    {
      "time": "04:02",
      "start": 242.55,
      "end": 244.86,
      "duration": 2.31,
      "text": "The first one is fitted\nwith a giant rocket engine,"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:04",
      "start": 244.86,
      "end": 247.77,
      "duration": 2.91,
      "text": "and the second one is fitted\nwith a very tiny rocket engine."
    },
    {
      "time": "04:07",
      "start": 247.77,
      "end": 249.84,
      "duration": 2.07,
      "text": "And let's say the first one produces"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:09",
      "start": 249.84,
      "end": 254.84,
      "duration": 5.0,
      "text": "an enormous thrust of a\n25, a thousand newtons,"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:15",
      "start": 255.33,
      "end": 258.69,
      "duration": 3.36,
      "text": "but that rocket will\nonly last for 0.1 second."
    },
    {
      "time": "04:18",
      "start": 258.69,
      "end": 261.085,
      "duration": 2.395,
      "text": "That thrust will only\nlast for 0.1 second, okay?"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:21",
      "start": 261.085,
      "end": 264.41999999999996,
      "duration": 3.335,
      "text": "The second one has a\nmuch more humble thrust,"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:24",
      "start": 264.42,
      "end": 269.19,
      "duration": 4.77,
      "text": "let's say only a mere 50 newtons,\nbut this rocket will last,"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:29",
      "start": 269.19,
      "end": 271.65,
      "duration": 2.46,
      "text": "this thrust will last for about a minute."
    },
    {
      "time": "04:31",
      "start": 271.65,
      "end": 272.96999999999997,
      "duration": 1.32,
      "text": "So now you can imagine this scenario,"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:32",
      "start": 272.97,
      "end": 275.43,
      "duration": 2.46,
      "text": "and the question is, if\nthese two cars are identical,"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:35",
      "start": 275.43,
      "end": 276.90000000000003,
      "duration": 1.47,
      "text": "they have the same mass and everything"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:36",
      "start": 276.9,
      "end": 278.72999999999996,
      "duration": 1.83,
      "text": "and they were initially at rest,"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:38",
      "start": 278.73,
      "end": 281.55,
      "duration": 2.82,
      "text": "then after their thrust ends,"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:41",
      "start": 281.55,
      "end": 284.97,
      "duration": 3.42,
      "text": "which car will have more speed?"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:44",
      "start": 284.97,
      "end": 287.07000000000005,
      "duration": 2.1,
      "text": "This one at the end of 0.1 seconds,"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:47",
      "start": 287.07,
      "end": 289.178,
      "duration": 2.108,
      "text": "or this one at the end of one minute?"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:49",
      "start": 289.178,
      "end": 291.401,
      "duration": 2.223,
      "text": "How would you answer that question?"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:51",
      "start": 291.401,
      "end": 294.54,
      "duration": 3.139,
      "text": "Well, if I didn't have\nthe idea of impulse,"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:54",
      "start": 294.54,
      "end": 297.51000000000005,
      "duration": 2.97,
      "text": "then I would think about,\nokay, I know the force,"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:57",
      "start": 297.51,
      "end": 300.36,
      "duration": 2.85,
      "text": "from that, I can try and\ncalculate the acceleration,"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:00",
      "start": 300.36,
      "end": 301.95,
      "duration": 1.59,
      "text": "and then after calculating\nthe acceleration,"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:01",
      "start": 301.95,
      "end": 304.56,
      "duration": 2.61,
      "text": "I'll try to figure out\nwhat the final velocity is."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:04",
      "start": 304.56,
      "end": 306.87,
      "duration": 2.31,
      "text": "Yuck, I'll have to do all\nof those calculations."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:06",
      "start": 306.87,
      "end": 309.0,
      "duration": 2.13,
      "text": "But you know what I can do now?"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:09",
      "start": 309.0,
      "end": 312.0,
      "duration": 3.0,
      "text": "Well, I can now say, hey\nlook, all I need to know"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:12",
      "start": 312.0,
      "end": 315.27,
      "duration": 3.27,
      "text": "is figure out which one\nhas more final momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:15",
      "start": 315.27,
      "end": 316.40999999999997,
      "duration": 1.14,
      "text": "In other words, I need to figure out"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:16",
      "start": 316.41,
      "end": 319.20000000000005,
      "duration": 2.79,
      "text": "which has more change in momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:19",
      "start": 319.2,
      "end": 320.84999999999997,
      "duration": 1.65,
      "text": "The one that has gained more momentum"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:20",
      "start": 320.85,
      "end": 322.65000000000003,
      "duration": 1.8,
      "text": "would definitely have more velocity."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:22",
      "start": 322.65,
      "end": 326.46,
      "duration": 3.81,
      "text": "And what decides that? What\ndecides that is impulse."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:26",
      "start": 326.46,
      "end": 330.75,
      "duration": 4.29,
      "text": "See, the change in momentum\nonly depends on the impulse."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:30",
      "start": 330.75,
      "end": 333.96,
      "duration": 3.21,
      "text": "So all I care about, I don't\ncare about the individual force"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:33",
      "start": 333.96,
      "end": 335.43,
      "duration": 1.47,
      "text": "and how long the force acts,"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:35",
      "start": 335.43,
      "end": 337.68,
      "duration": 2.25,
      "text": "I care about the product\nbecause it's the product"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:37",
      "start": 337.68,
      "end": 339.39,
      "duration": 1.71,
      "text": "that decides the change in momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:39",
      "start": 339.39,
      "end": 341.64,
      "duration": 2.25,
      "text": "So in my head, I'm now thinking, \"Hey,"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:41",
      "start": 341.64,
      "end": 344.37,
      "duration": 2.73,
      "text": "whichever has the bigger product"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:44",
      "start": 344.37,
      "end": 346.77,
      "duration": 2.4,
      "text": "will end up having a\nbigger change in momentum,"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:46",
      "start": 346.77,
      "end": 349.97999999999996,
      "duration": 3.21,
      "text": "and therefore, we'll end up\nhaving a bigger final velocity.\""
    },
    {
      "time": "05:49",
      "start": 349.98,
      "end": 352.29,
      "duration": 2.31,
      "text": "So which one has the more bigger product?"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:52",
      "start": 352.29,
      "end": 354.27000000000004,
      "duration": 1.98,
      "text": "Which one has a higher\nimpulse? Well, let's see."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:54",
      "start": 354.27,
      "end": 357.12,
      "duration": 2.85,
      "text": "Well for the first one, the\nimpulse and the unit, sorry,"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:57",
      "start": 357.12,
      "end": 359.79,
      "duration": 2.67,
      "text": "the symbol that we use for impulse is J."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:59",
      "start": 359.79,
      "end": 361.62,
      "duration": 1.83,
      "text": "Don't ask me at this point (laughs)"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:01",
      "start": 361.62,
      "end": 365.7,
      "duration": 4.08,
      "text": "why we use J for impulse, but\nI think that's what we use."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:05",
      "start": 365.7,
      "end": 367.05,
      "duration": 1.35,
      "text": "But what is impulse over here?"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:07",
      "start": 367.05,
      "end": 370.2,
      "duration": 3.15,
      "text": "It's force multiplied by the\ntime on which that force acts."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:10",
      "start": 370.2,
      "end": 374.09999999999997,
      "duration": 3.9,
      "text": "So it forces 25,000\nnewtons multiplied by 0.1,"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:14",
      "start": 374.1,
      "end": 376.08000000000004,
      "duration": 1.98,
      "text": "well that become one decimal will shift,"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:16",
      "start": 376.08,
      "end": 381.08,
      "duration": 5.0,
      "text": "it will be 2,500 newton seconds,\nthat's the impulse here."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:21",
      "start": 381.09,
      "end": 383.46,
      "duration": 2.37,
      "text": "And of course, impulse\nis a vector quantity,"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:23",
      "start": 383.46,
      "end": 385.34999999999997,
      "duration": 1.89,
      "text": "which means its direction is important,"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:25",
      "start": 385.35,
      "end": 387.09000000000003,
      "duration": 1.74,
      "text": "and since the force is to the right,"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:27",
      "start": 387.09,
      "end": 388.89,
      "duration": 1.8,
      "text": "the thrust is to the right over here,"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:28",
      "start": 388.89,
      "end": 392.76,
      "duration": 3.87,
      "text": "that means the impulse will\nalso be to the right direction."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:32",
      "start": 392.76,
      "end": 395.96999999999997,
      "duration": 3.21,
      "text": "This means its momentum will\nchange towards the right,"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:35",
      "start": 395.97,
      "end": 398.07000000000005,
      "duration": 2.1,
      "text": "it'll gain momentum\ntowards the right side,"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:38",
      "start": 398.07,
      "end": 399.705,
      "duration": 1.635,
      "text": "and that makes sense."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:39",
      "start": 399.705,
      "end": 401.7,
      "duration": 1.995,
      "text": "And what's the impulse here?"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:41",
      "start": 401.7,
      "end": 403.96299999999997,
      "duration": 2.263,
      "text": "Well, the impulse over here is going to be"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:43",
      "start": 403.963,
      "end": 406.74,
      "duration": 2.777,
      "text": "same thing, force multiplied by time."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:46",
      "start": 406.74,
      "end": 408.51,
      "duration": 1.77,
      "text": "Well, the time now, if I use seconds,"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:48",
      "start": 408.51,
      "end": 410.90999999999997,
      "duration": 2.4,
      "text": "as you used second over\nhere, so 60 seconds,"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:50",
      "start": 410.91,
      "end": 414.42,
      "duration": 3.51,
      "text": "so 50 times 60, five, six, zero, 30,"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:54",
      "start": 414.42,
      "end": 417.326,
      "duration": 2.906,
      "text": "that's 3000 newton, second."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:57",
      "start": 417.326,
      "end": 419.85,
      "duration": 2.524,
      "text": "(gasps) Look at that!"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:59",
      "start": 419.85,
      "end": 423.367,
      "duration": 3.517,
      "text": "This has a bigger impulse,\nso now I can immediately say,"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:03",
      "start": 423.367,
      "end": 428.367,
      "duration": 5.0,
      "text": "\"Aha,\" therefore this will have\na larger change in momentum,"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:08",
      "start": 428.37,
      "end": 431.242,
      "duration": 2.872,
      "text": "therefore this car will be faster"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:11",
      "start": 431.242,
      "end": 433.83000000000004,
      "duration": 2.588,
      "text": "at the end of its thrust\ncompared to this car."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:13",
      "start": 433.83,
      "end": 435.41999999999996,
      "duration": 1.59,
      "text": "Isn't that amazing?"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:15",
      "start": 435.42,
      "end": 437.46000000000004,
      "duration": 2.04,
      "text": "I could literally do this in my head."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:17",
      "start": 437.46,
      "end": 439.73999999999995,
      "duration": 2.28,
      "text": "Without having to do\na lot of calculations,"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:19",
      "start": 439.74,
      "end": 441.33,
      "duration": 1.59,
      "text": "I could answer that question."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:21",
      "start": 441.33,
      "end": 444.18,
      "duration": 2.85,
      "text": "So remember, what decides\nthe change in momentum?"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:24",
      "start": 444.18,
      "end": 445.62,
      "duration": 1.44,
      "text": "It's not the force alone,"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:25",
      "start": 445.62,
      "end": 447.96,
      "duration": 2.34,
      "text": "not the time alone, it's the product."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:27",
      "start": 447.96,
      "end": 449.54999999999995,
      "duration": 1.59,
      "text": "So whenever you wanna think about"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:29",
      "start": 449.55,
      "end": 451.89,
      "duration": 2.34,
      "text": "how much the momentum\nchanges, all you gotta say is,"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:31",
      "start": 451.89,
      "end": 453.36,
      "duration": 1.47,
      "text": "I just wanna care about that product."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:33",
      "start": 453.36,
      "end": 456.3,
      "duration": 2.94,
      "text": "How much is the product?\nHow much is the impulse?"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:36",
      "start": 456.3,
      "end": 458.55,
      "duration": 2.25,
      "text": "All right, another\nexample, another question,"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:38",
      "start": 458.55,
      "end": 461.04,
      "duration": 2.49,
      "text": "you drop a couple of eggs\nfrom the same height,"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:41",
      "start": 461.04,
      "end": 462.6,
      "duration": 1.56,
      "text": "one on a very hard rock,"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:42",
      "start": 462.6,
      "end": 465.63,
      "duration": 3.03,
      "text": "and the other one on a very soft pillow."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:45",
      "start": 465.63,
      "end": 467.82,
      "duration": 2.19,
      "text": "We know the one that lands\non a rock will crack,"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:47",
      "start": 467.82,
      "end": 469.53,
      "duration": 1.71,
      "text": "but the one that will\nland on the soft pillow"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:49",
      "start": 469.53,
      "end": 471.98199999999997,
      "duration": 2.452,
      "text": "will probably not, why?"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:51",
      "start": 471.982,
      "end": 475.17,
      "duration": 3.188,
      "text": "Well we might think that it's\nbecause it's softer. (laughs)"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:55",
      "start": 475.17,
      "end": 476.88,
      "duration": 1.71,
      "text": "You know, if you have softer things,"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:56",
      "start": 476.88,
      "end": 478.92,
      "duration": 2.04,
      "text": "well it cushions and it doesn't, you know,"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:58",
      "start": 478.92,
      "end": 480.72,
      "duration": 1.8,
      "text": "the forces over here would be smaller,"
    },
    {
      "time": "08:00",
      "start": 480.72,
      "end": 483.21000000000004,
      "duration": 2.49,
      "text": "compared to over here, but why?"
    },
    {
      "time": "08:03",
      "start": 483.21,
      "end": 484.68,
      "duration": 1.47,
      "text": "Think about why."
    },
    {
      "time": "08:04",
      "start": 484.68,
      "end": 487.74,
      "duration": 3.06,
      "text": "We can now answer that question\nusing the idea of impulse."
    },
    {
      "time": "08:07",
      "start": 487.74,
      "end": 489.75,
      "duration": 2.01,
      "text": "Think about it, because they were dropped"
    },
    {
      "time": "08:09",
      "start": 489.75,
      "end": 492.42,
      "duration": 2.67,
      "text": "from the same height, just before hitting,"
    },
    {
      "time": "08:12",
      "start": 492.42,
      "end": 497.19,
      "duration": 4.77,
      "text": "just before these eggs hit\nthe rock or the pillow,"
    },
    {
      "time": "08:17",
      "start": 497.19,
      "end": 498.33,
      "duration": 1.14,
      "text": "they had the same velocity"
    },
    {
      "time": "08:18",
      "start": 498.33,
      "end": 499.53,
      "duration": 1.2,
      "text": "because they were dropped\nfrom the same height,"
    },
    {
      "time": "08:19",
      "start": 499.53,
      "end": 501.05999999999995,
      "duration": 1.53,
      "text": "so they had the same velocity, right?"
    },
    {
      "time": "08:21",
      "start": 501.06,
      "end": 504.298,
      "duration": 3.238,
      "text": "Which means they had the same\nmomentum, initial momentum,"
    },
    {
      "time": "08:24",
      "start": 504.298,
      "end": 506.97,
      "duration": 2.672,
      "text": "just before hitting was exactly the same."
    },
    {
      "time": "08:26",
      "start": 506.97,
      "end": 508.20000000000005,
      "duration": 1.23,
      "text": "What happens after hitting?"
    },
    {
      "time": "08:28",
      "start": 508.2,
      "end": 510.3,
      "duration": 2.1,
      "text": "Will their momentum again\nwill become the same"
    },
    {
      "time": "08:30",
      "start": 510.3,
      "end": 512.76,
      "duration": 2.46,
      "text": "because their momentum will be\nzero, they'll come to a stop."
    },
    {
      "time": "08:32",
      "start": 512.76,
      "end": 515.91,
      "duration": 3.15,
      "text": "This will crack, of course, but\ntheir momentum becomes zero,"
    },
    {
      "time": "08:35",
      "start": 515.91,
      "end": 517.7099999999999,
      "duration": 1.8,
      "text": "which means the initial\nmomentum are the same,"
    },
    {
      "time": "08:37",
      "start": 517.71,
      "end": 519.21,
      "duration": 1.5,
      "text": "the final momentum are the same,"
    },
    {
      "time": "08:39",
      "start": 519.21,
      "end": 521.82,
      "duration": 2.61,
      "text": "so their change in momentum is the same."
    },
    {
      "time": "08:41",
      "start": 521.82,
      "end": 524.19,
      "duration": 2.37,
      "text": "In other words, the change\nin momentum is the same."
    },
    {
      "time": "08:44",
      "start": 524.19,
      "end": 526.5,
      "duration": 2.31,
      "text": "The impulse delivered to both these eggs"
    },
    {
      "time": "08:46",
      "start": 526.5,
      "end": 528.42,
      "duration": 1.92,
      "text": "are exactly the same."
    },
    {
      "time": "08:48",
      "start": 528.42,
      "end": 529.62,
      "duration": 1.2,
      "text": "Ooh, interesting."
    },
    {
      "time": "08:49",
      "start": 529.62,
      "end": 534.62,
      "duration": 5.0,
      "text": "So the impulse here is exactly\nthe same as the impulse here."
    },
    {
      "time": "08:54",
      "start": 534.72,
      "end": 539.139,
      "duration": 4.419,
      "text": "And I'm talking about impulse\nat the point of impact, okay?"
    },
    {
      "time": "08:59",
      "start": 539.139,
      "end": 542.55,
      "duration": 3.411,
      "text": "The impulse is exactly the\nsame, but there's a difference"
    },
    {
      "time": "09:02",
      "start": 542.55,
      "end": 544.89,
      "duration": 2.34,
      "text": "between the impulse here\nand the impulse here."
    },
    {
      "time": "09:04",
      "start": 544.89,
      "end": 547.17,
      "duration": 2.28,
      "text": "The difference is, when\nyou land on a pillow,"
    },
    {
      "time": "09:07",
      "start": 547.17,
      "end": 549.6899999999999,
      "duration": 2.52,
      "text": "because the pillow is soft,"
    },
    {
      "time": "09:09",
      "start": 549.69,
      "end": 552.48,
      "duration": 2.79,
      "text": "it gives a little bit, it can deform."
    },
    {
      "time": "09:12",
      "start": 552.48,
      "end": 553.654,
      "duration": 1.174,
      "text": "Because it can deform,"
    },
    {
      "time": "09:13",
      "start": 553.654,
      "end": 557.85,
      "duration": 4.196,
      "text": "the egg can actually get\nembedded a little bit over there,"
    },
    {
      "time": "09:17",
      "start": 557.85,
      "end": 560.49,
      "duration": 2.64,
      "text": "it can travel a little\nbit more over there,"
    },
    {
      "time": "09:20",
      "start": 560.49,
      "end": 564.42,
      "duration": 3.93,
      "text": "which means it takes more\ntime for the egg to stop."
    },
    {
      "time": "09:24",
      "start": 564.42,
      "end": 567.78,
      "duration": 3.36,
      "text": "In other words, because it is softer,"
    },
    {
      "time": "09:27",
      "start": 567.78,
      "end": 572.37,
      "duration": 4.59,
      "text": "the time over which that\nmomentum changed was large."
    },
    {
      "time": "09:32",
      "start": 572.37,
      "end": 575.34,
      "duration": 2.97,
      "text": "It took more time for that egg to stop."
    },
    {
      "time": "09:35",
      "start": 575.34,
      "end": 578.76,
      "duration": 3.42,
      "text": "Compared to over here, the\nrock is not soft at all,"
    },
    {
      "time": "09:38",
      "start": 578.76,
      "end": 580.56,
      "duration": 1.8,
      "text": "it's very hard, which\nmeans it doesn't give,"
    },
    {
      "time": "09:40",
      "start": 580.56,
      "end": 582.81,
      "duration": 2.25,
      "text": "it doesn't allow it to embed itself."
    },
    {
      "time": "09:42",
      "start": 582.81,
      "end": 586.2299999999999,
      "duration": 3.42,
      "text": "It doesn't deform, and so the\negg almost stops instantly."
    },
    {
      "time": "09:46",
      "start": 586.23,
      "end": 589.2,
      "duration": 2.97,
      "text": "In other words, the time over\nwhich that impulse acted,"
    },
    {
      "time": "09:49",
      "start": 589.2,
      "end": 591.884,
      "duration": 2.684,
      "text": "the force acted, was very tiny."
    },
    {
      "time": "09:51",
      "start": 591.884,
      "end": 593.94,
      "duration": 2.056,
      "text": "Now think about this,"
    },
    {
      "time": "09:53",
      "start": 593.94,
      "end": 596.1,
      "duration": 2.16,
      "text": "we know the impulse has to be the same,"
    },
    {
      "time": "09:56",
      "start": 596.1,
      "end": 598.5600000000001,
      "duration": 2.46,
      "text": "this means the product of the force"
    },
    {
      "time": "09:58",
      "start": 598.56,
      "end": 600.51,
      "duration": 1.95,
      "text": "and the time must be the same,"
    },
    {
      "time": "10:00",
      "start": 600.51,
      "end": 603.24,
      "duration": 2.73,
      "text": "which means if the time is bigger,"
    },
    {
      "time": "10:03",
      "start": 603.24,
      "end": 604.6800000000001,
      "duration": 1.44,
      "text": "the force will be smaller."
    },
    {
      "time": "10:04",
      "start": 604.68,
      "end": 608.13,
      "duration": 3.45,
      "text": "If the time is smaller,\nthe force will be bigger."
    },
    {
      "time": "10:08",
      "start": 608.13,
      "end": 611.9399999999999,
      "duration": 3.81,
      "text": "So notice over here, because\nthe time is big, the force,"
    },
    {
      "time": "10:11",
      "start": 611.94,
      "end": 616.5300000000001,
      "duration": 4.59,
      "text": "the net force acting over\nhere, would be very tiny."
    },
    {
      "time": "10:16",
      "start": 616.53,
      "end": 619.1999999999999,
      "duration": 2.67,
      "text": "But since the time over\nhere is much smaller,"
    },
    {
      "time": "10:19",
      "start": 619.2,
      "end": 623.1,
      "duration": 3.9,
      "text": "the net force acting\nover here is much bigger."
    },
    {
      "time": "10:23",
      "start": 623.1,
      "end": 626.94,
      "duration": 3.84,
      "text": "And there you go, now we\nunderstand exactly why"
    },
    {
      "time": "10:26",
      "start": 626.94,
      "end": 629.6700000000001,
      "duration": 2.73,
      "text": "hard things put a bigger force"
    },
    {
      "time": "10:29",
      "start": 629.67,
      "end": 632.7299999999999,
      "duration": 3.06,
      "text": "because the momentum changes very quickly."
    },
    {
      "time": "10:32",
      "start": 632.73,
      "end": 636.0600000000001,
      "duration": 3.33,
      "text": "And then when you have an\nimpulse with a very small time,"
    },
    {
      "time": "10:36",
      "start": 636.06,
      "end": 638.43,
      "duration": 2.37,
      "text": "we get a much bigger force."
    },
    {
      "time": "10:38",
      "start": 638.43,
      "end": 639.63,
      "duration": 1.2,
      "text": "Isn't that amazing?"
    },
    {
      "time": "10:39",
      "start": 639.63,
      "end": 642.06,
      "duration": 2.43,
      "text": "So long story short, if\nyou want things to crack,"
    },
    {
      "time": "10:42",
      "start": 642.06,
      "end": 645.0,
      "duration": 2.94,
      "text": "well make sure you have\nvery hard collisions."
    },
    {
      "time": "10:45",
      "start": 645.0,
      "end": 647.7,
      "duration": 2.7,
      "text": "This means that make the\ntime of contact very small,"
    },
    {
      "time": "10:47",
      "start": 647.7,
      "end": 649.71,
      "duration": 2.01,
      "text": "make the momentum change very quickly,"
    },
    {
      "time": "10:49",
      "start": 649.71,
      "end": 652.71,
      "duration": 3.0,
      "text": "you'll end up having big\nforces, you can break things."
    },
    {
      "time": "10:52",
      "start": 652.71,
      "end": 655.77,
      "duration": 3.06,
      "text": "On the other hand, if you\ndon't want to break things,"
    },
    {
      "time": "10:55",
      "start": 655.77,
      "end": 658.71,
      "duration": 2.94,
      "text": "you want to have softer collisions,"
    },
    {
      "time": "10:58",
      "start": 658.71,
      "end": 662.442,
      "duration": 3.732,
      "text": "which means you want the time\nof impact to be much bigger,"
    },
    {
      "time": "11:02",
      "start": 662.442,
      "end": 666.9,
      "duration": 4.458,
      "text": "and therefore, the force ends\nup becoming much smaller."
    },
    {
      "time": "11:06",
      "start": 666.9,
      "end": 668.101,
      "duration": 1.201,
      "text": "Beautiful, right?"
    },
    {
      "time": "11:08",
      "start": 668.101,
      "end": 670.68,
      "duration": 2.579,
      "text": "Now we can come back to\nour original question."
    },
    {
      "time": "11:10",
      "start": 670.68,
      "end": 672.87,
      "duration": 2.19,
      "text": "Let's say our car was\nmade up of very strong,"
    },
    {
      "time": "11:12",
      "start": 672.87,
      "end": 674.73,
      "duration": 1.86,
      "text": "almost indestructible material."
    },
    {
      "time": "11:14",
      "start": 674.73,
      "end": 677.19,
      "duration": 2.46,
      "text": "Then what happens when it\ngoes and just rams into it?"
    },
    {
      "time": "11:17",
      "start": 677.19,
      "end": 680.0400000000001,
      "duration": 2.85,
      "text": "Well, it's gonna stop almost instantly,"
    },
    {
      "time": "11:20",
      "start": 680.04,
      "end": 682.5,
      "duration": 2.46,
      "text": "just like the toy cars\nthat we have over here,"
    },
    {
      "time": "11:22",
      "start": 682.5,
      "end": 684.06,
      "duration": 1.56,
      "text": "or maybe it'll bounce back."
    },
    {
      "time": "11:24",
      "start": 684.06,
      "end": 686.6429999999999,
      "duration": 2.583,
      "text": "But in all that case,\nwhat happens is the time"
    },
    {
      "time": "11:26",
      "start": 686.643,
      "end": 689.9100000000001,
      "duration": 3.267,
      "text": "over which that collision\nlasted would be very tiny,"
    },
    {
      "time": "11:29",
      "start": 689.91,
      "end": 690.8399999999999,
      "duration": 0.93,
      "text": "just like over here."
    },
    {
      "time": "11:30",
      "start": 690.84,
      "end": 693.4200000000001,
      "duration": 2.58,
      "text": "So we are dealing with a\nhard collision over here,"
    },
    {
      "time": "11:33",
      "start": 693.42,
      "end": 697.65,
      "duration": 4.23,
      "text": "meaning we are dealing with\nmuch larger forces of collision."
    },
    {
      "time": "11:37",
      "start": 697.65,
      "end": 698.73,
      "duration": 1.08,
      "text": "Now that's not bad for the car"
    },
    {
      "time": "11:38",
      "start": 698.73,
      "end": 700.62,
      "duration": 1.89,
      "text": "because the car is made of\nindestructible material,"
    },
    {
      "time": "11:40",
      "start": 700.62,
      "end": 701.79,
      "duration": 1.17,
      "text": "but that's bad for us"
    },
    {
      "time": "11:41",
      "start": 701.79,
      "end": 705.5699999999999,
      "duration": 3.78,
      "text": "because even we will stop\nalmost instantly, and therefore,"
    },
    {
      "time": "11:45",
      "start": 705.57,
      "end": 708.48,
      "duration": 2.91,
      "text": "the forces acting on us\nwill also be much larger."
    },
    {
      "time": "11:48",
      "start": 708.48,
      "end": 709.95,
      "duration": 1.47,
      "text": "That's bad for us."
    },
    {
      "time": "11:49",
      "start": 709.95,
      "end": 713.3100000000001,
      "duration": 3.36,
      "text": "On the other hand, what if the\ncar has some crumple zones?"
    },
    {
      "time": "11:53",
      "start": 713.31,
      "end": 715.29,
      "duration": 1.98,
      "text": "Well then what happens\nis that that crumple zone"
    },
    {
      "time": "11:55",
      "start": 715.29,
      "end": 719.79,
      "duration": 4.5,
      "text": "will allow that car to\ntravel slightly further"
    },
    {
      "time": "11:59",
      "start": 719.79,
      "end": 721.38,
      "duration": 1.59,
      "text": "before coming to a stop."
    },
    {
      "time": "12:01",
      "start": 721.38,
      "end": 723.42,
      "duration": 2.04,
      "text": "In other words, it allows that car"
    },
    {
      "time": "12:03",
      "start": 723.42,
      "end": 727.1999999999999,
      "duration": 3.78,
      "text": "to take more time before coming to a stop,"
    },
    {
      "time": "12:07",
      "start": 727.2,
      "end": 730.38,
      "duration": 3.18,
      "text": "kind of like what happened over here."
    },
    {
      "time": "12:10",
      "start": 730.38,
      "end": 735.21,
      "duration": 4.83,
      "text": "Because of that, the time\nof collision is increased,"
    },
    {
      "time": "12:15",
      "start": 735.21,
      "end": 736.5600000000001,
      "duration": 1.35,
      "text": "and as a result,"
    },
    {
      "time": "12:16",
      "start": 736.56,
      "end": 739.38,
      "duration": 2.82,
      "text": "the forces acting over\nhere will be much smaller."
    },
    {
      "time": "12:19",
      "start": 739.38,
      "end": 740.73,
      "duration": 1.35,
      "text": "Now because the car is fragile,"
    },
    {
      "time": "12:20",
      "start": 740.73,
      "end": 742.59,
      "duration": 1.86,
      "text": "the car gets damaged, but that's fine,"
    },
    {
      "time": "12:22",
      "start": 742.59,
      "end": 744.7800000000001,
      "duration": 2.19,
      "text": "but even smaller forces\nwill be acting on us"
    },
    {
      "time": "12:24",
      "start": 744.78,
      "end": 749.4599999999999,
      "duration": 4.68,
      "text": "compared to over here, and\ntherefore, this is much safer."
    },
    {
      "time": "12:29",
      "start": 749.46,
      "end": 751.23,
      "duration": 1.77,
      "text": "And you can now see how airbags"
    },
    {
      "time": "12:31",
      "start": 751.23,
      "end": 754.02,
      "duration": 2.79,
      "text": "will further increase the time over which"
    },
    {
      "time": "12:34",
      "start": 754.02,
      "end": 756.75,
      "duration": 2.73,
      "text": "our bodies come to a stop,\nfurther increase this number,"
    },
    {
      "time": "12:36",
      "start": 756.75,
      "end": 760.35,
      "duration": 3.6,
      "text": "further reducing the net\nforce acting on our bodies."
    },
    {
      "time": "12:40",
      "start": 760.35,
      "end": 761.6,
      "duration": 1.25,
      "text": "Beautiful idea, isn't it?"
    }
  ]
}